  <para style="mt1">1 <char style="add">&gt;ones</char>_from_Thessalonikaʸ</para>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="1TH 1" />
  <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1TH 1:1" />Paulos, and Silouanos, and Timotheos, to_the assembly of_<char style="add">+the</char>_<char style="add">&gt;ones</char>_from_Thessalonikaʸ in <char style="nd">god</char> <char style="add">+the</char>_father and <char style="add">+the</char>_<char style="nd">master</char> <char style="nd">Yaʸsous/(Yəhōshūˊa)</char> <char style="nd">chosen_one/messiah</char>: grace to_you_all and peace. <verse eid="1TH 1:1" /><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1TH 1:2" />We_are_giving_thanks to_<char style="nd">god</char> always concerning all of_you_all, remembrance making in the prayers of_us, unceasingly <verse eid="1TH 1:2" /><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1TH 1:3" />remembering of_you_all about_the work of_faith, and the labor of_love, and the endurance of_hope of_the <char style="nd">master</char> of_us, <char style="nd">Yaʸsous</char> <char style="nd">chosen_one</char>, before the <char style="nd">god</char> and father of_us, <verse eid="1TH 1:3" /><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1TH 1:4" />having_known, brothers having_been_loved by <char style="nd">god</char>, the choice of_you_all, <verse eid="1TH 1:4" /><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1TH 1:5" />because the good_message of_us not was_become to you_all in message only, but also in power, and in <char style="add">+the</char>_<char style="nd">spirit</char> holy, and full_assurance much, as you_all_have_known such_as we_were_become you_all because_of you_all. <verse eid="1TH 1:5" /><verse number="6" style="v" sid="1TH 1:6" />And you_all imitators of_us were_become and of_the <char style="nd">master</char>, having_received the message in tribulation much with <char style="add">+the</char>_joy of_<char style="add">+the</char>_<char style="nd">spirit</char> holy, <verse eid="1TH 1:6" /><verse number="7" style="v" sid="1TH 1:7" />so_as to_become you_all examples to_all the <char style="add">&gt;ones</char> believing in Makedonia and in Aⱪaia. <verse eid="1TH 1:7" /><verse number="8" style="v" sid="1TH 1:8" />From for you_all has_been_sounded_out the message of_the <char style="nd">master</char>, not only in Makedonia and in Aⱪaia, but in every place the faith of_you_all toward <char style="nd">god</char> has_come_out, so_as no need to_be_having us to_be_speaking anything. <verse eid="1TH 1:8" /><verse number="9" style="v" sid="1TH 1:9" />For they concerning us are_reporting what_kind entrance we_had to you_all, and how you_all_turned_back to <char style="nd">god</char> from idols, to_be_serving for_<char style="add">+the</char>_<char style="nd">god</char> living and true, <verse eid="1TH 1:9" /><verse number="10" style="v" sid="1TH 1:10" />and to_be_waiting for_the son of_him from the heavens, whom he_raised from the dead, <char style="nd">Yaʸsous</char>, the <char style="add">&gt;one</char> rescuing us from the severe_anger coming.<chapter eid="1TH 1" /><chapter number="2" style="c" sid="1TH 2" /><verse eid="1TH 1:10" /><verse number="1" style="v" sid="1TH 2:1" />For yourselves you_all_have_known, brothers, the entrance of_us to you_all, that not vain it_has_become, <verse eid="1TH 2:1" /><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1TH 2:2" />but having_previously_suffered and having_been_mistreated, as you_all_have_known, in Filippou we_spoke_boldly in the <char style="nd">god</char> of_us, to_speak to you_all the good_message of_<char style="nd">god</char> among much struggle. <verse eid="1TH 2:2" /><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1TH 2:3" />For the exhortation of_us not of deception, nor of impurity, nor in deceit, <verse eid="1TH 2:3" /><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1TH 2:4" />but as we_have_been_approved by <char style="nd">god</char>, to_be_entrusted the good_message, thus we_are_speaking, not as to_people bringing_pleasure, but to_<char style="nd">god</char>, the <char style="add">&gt;one</char> approving the hearts of_us. <verse eid="1TH 2:4" /><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1TH 2:5" />For neither once with message of_flattery we_were_become, as you_all_have_known, nor with <char style="add">+a</char>_under_pretense for_greediness (<char style="nd">god</char> <char style="add">=is</char> witness) <verse eid="1TH 2:5" /><verse number="6" style="v" sid="1TH 2:6" />nor seeking from people glory, neither from you_all, nor from others, <verse eid="1TH 2:6" /><verse number="7" style="v" sid="1TH 2:7" />being_able in burden to_be, as of_<char style="nd">chosen_one/messiah</char> ambassadors. But we_were_become infants in <char style="add">+the</char>_midst of_you_all, as <char style="add">+a</char>_nursing_mother may_be_cherishing the of_herself children. <verse eid="1TH 2:7" /><verse number="8" style="v" sid="1TH 2:8" />Thus longing for_you_all, we_were_taking_pleasure to_share with_you_all, not only the good_message of_<char style="nd">god</char>, but also the of_ourselves lives, because beloved to_us you_all_were_become. <verse eid="1TH 2:8" /><verse number="9" style="v" sid="1TH 2:9" />For you_all_are_remembering, brothers, the labor of_us and hardship, night and day working, in_order that not to_burden anyone of_you_all, we_proclaimed to you_all the good_message of_<char style="nd">god</char>. <verse eid="1TH 2:9" /><verse number="10" style="v" sid="1TH 2:10" />You_all <char style="add">=are</char> witnesses and <char style="nd">god</char>, how devoutly, and justly, and blamelessly, to_you_all the <char style="add">&gt;ones</char> believing we_were_become, <verse eid="1TH 2:10" /><verse number="11" style="v" sid="1TH 2:11" />just_as you_all_have_known how one each of_you_all, as <char style="add">+a</char>_father to_children of_himself, <verse eid="1TH 2:11" /><verse number="12" style="v" sid="1TH 2:12" />exhorting you_all, and consoling, and testifying, in_order that to_be_walking you_all worthily of_<char style="nd">god</char>, the <char style="add">&gt;one</char> having_called you_all into the of_himself kingdom and glory. <verse eid="1TH 2:12" /><verse number="13" style="v" sid="1TH 2:13" />And because_of this also we are_giving_thanks to_<char style="nd">god</char> unceasingly that having_received <char style="add">+the</char>_message by_hearing from us of_<char style="nd">god</char>, you_all_received not <char style="add">+the</char>_message of_humans, but as truly it_is, <char style="add">+the</char>_message of_<char style="nd">god</char>, which also is_working in you_all believing. <verse eid="1TH 2:13" /><verse number="14" style="v" sid="1TH 2:14" />For you_all imitators were_become, brothers, of_the assemblies of_<char style="nd">god</char>, being in Youdaia in <char style="nd">chosen_one</char> <char style="nd">Yaʸsous/(Yəhōshūˊa)</char>, because the same <char style="add">&gt;things</char> you_all_suffered, also you_all by your own fellow-countrymen, as also they <char style="add">did</char> by the Youdaiōns, <verse eid="1TH 2:14" /><verse number="15" style="v" sid="1TH 2:15" />who both the <char style="nd">master</char> having_killed_off <char style="nd">Yaʸsous</char>, and their prophets, and us having_driven_out, and to_<char style="nd">god</char> not bringing_pleasure, but to_all people of_contrary, <verse eid="1TH 2:15" /><verse number="16" style="v" sid="1TH 2:16" />forbidding us to_the pagans to_speak, in_order_that they_may_be_saved, for which to_fulfill of_them the sins always. But came on them the severe_anger to end. <verse eid="1TH 2:16" /><verse number="17" style="v" sid="1TH 2:17" />But we, brothers, having_been_orphaned of you_all, for <char style="add">+the</char>_time of_<char style="add">+an</char>_hour, in_face not in_heart, more_abundantly we_were_earnest the face of_you_all to_see with great desire. <verse eid="1TH 2:17" /><verse number="18" style="v" sid="1TH 2:18" />Because we_wanted to_come to you_all, I indeed Paulos, both once and twice, and hindered us Satan/(Sāţān). <verse eid="1TH 2:18" /><verse number="19" style="v" sid="1TH 2:19" />For who <char style="add">=is</char> of_us <char style="add">+the</char>_hope or <char style="add">+the</char>_joy or <char style="add">+the</char>_crown of_boasting? Or not <char style="add">=are</char> even you_all, before the <char style="nd">master</char> of_us, <char style="nd">Yaʸsous</char>, at the of_him coming? <verse eid="1TH 2:19" /><verse number="20" style="v" sid="1TH 2:20" />For you_all are the glory of_us, and <char style="add">+the</char>_joy.<chapter eid="1TH 2" /><chapter number="3" style="c" sid="1TH 3" /><verse eid="1TH 2:20" /><verse number="1" style="v" sid="1TH 3:1" />Therefore no_longer enduring, we_took_pleasure to_be_left in Athaʸnai only, <verse eid="1TH 3:1" /><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1TH 3:2" />and we_sent Timotheos, the brother of_us, and servant of_<char style="nd">god</char> in the good_message of_the <char style="nd">chosen_one/messiah</char>, in_order that to_strengthen you_all and to_exhort, concerning the faith of_you_all, <verse eid="1TH 3:2" /><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1TH 3:3" />that no_one to_be_being_disturbed by tribulations these. For yourselves you_all_have_known that for this we_are_appointing. <verse eid="1TH 3:3" /><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1TH 3:4" />For also when with you_all we_were, we_were_previously_saying to_you_all that we_are_going to_be_being_oppressed, as also it_became and you_all_have_known. <verse eid="1TH 3:4" /><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1TH 3:5" />Because_of this also_I no_longer enduring, I_sent in_order that to_know the faith of_you_all, lest somehow tempted you_all the <char style="add">&gt;one</char> tempting, and in vain may_become the labor of_us. <verse eid="1TH 3:5" /><verse number="6" style="v" sid="1TH 3:6" />But now having_come Timotheos to us from you_all, and having_good_message_preached to_us about_the faith and the love of_you_all, and that you_all_are_having <char style="add">+a</char>_mentioning of_us good always, longing us to_see, just_as also we you_all. <verse eid="1TH 3:6" /><verse number="7" style="v" sid="1TH 3:7" />Because_of this we_were_comforted, brothers, by you_all in all the distress and tribulation of_us, through the of_you_all faith. <verse eid="1TH 3:7" /><verse number="8" style="v" sid="1TH 3:8" />Because now we_are_living, if you_all are_standing_firm in <char style="add">+the</char>_<char style="nd">master</char>. <verse eid="1TH 3:8" /><verse number="9" style="v" sid="1TH 3:9" />For what thanksgiving we_are_being_able to_the to_<char style="nd">god</char> to_repay concerning you_all, for all the joy that we_are_rejoicing because_of you_all, before the <char style="nd">god</char> of_us. <verse eid="1TH 3:9" /><verse number="10" style="v" sid="1TH 3:10" />Night and day, beyond_exceedingly beseeching in_order that to_see of_you_all the face, and to_prepare the lacking <char style="add">&gt;things</char> in_<char style="add">+the</char>_faith of_you_all? <verse eid="1TH 3:10" /><verse number="11" style="v" sid="1TH 3:11" />And himself the <char style="nd">god</char> and father of_us, and the <char style="nd">master</char> of_us, <char style="nd">Yaʸsous/(Yəhōshūˊa)</char>, might_direct the way of_us to you_all. <verse eid="1TH 3:11" /><verse number="12" style="v" sid="1TH 3:12" />And you_all the <char style="nd">master</char> might_abound and might_abound in_love toward one_another, and toward all, just_as also we toward you_all, <verse eid="1TH 3:12" /><verse number="13" style="v" sid="1TH 3:13" />in_order that to_strengthen of_you_all the hearts, blameless in holiness before the <char style="nd">god</char> and father of_us, at the coming of_the <char style="nd">master</char> of_us, <char style="nd">Yaʸsous</char>, with all the holy <char style="add">&gt;ones</char> of_him. Truly.<chapter eid="1TH 3" /><chapter number="4" style="c" sid="1TH 4" /><verse eid="1TH 3:13" /><verse number="1" style="v" sid="1TH 4:1" />Therefore finally, brothers, we_are_asking you_all and we_are_exhorting in the <char style="add">+the</char>_<char style="nd">master</char> <char style="nd">Yaʸsous</char>, as you_all_received from us, how it_is_fitting you_all to_be_walking and to_be_bringing_pleasure to_<char style="nd">god</char> (as even you_all_are_walking), in_order_that you_all_may_be_abounding more. <verse eid="1TH 4:1" /><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1TH 4:2" />For you_all_have_known what_all charges we_gave to_you_all through the <char style="nd">master</char> <char style="nd">Yaʸsous</char>. <verse eid="1TH 4:2" /><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1TH 4:3" />For this is <char style="add">+the</char>_will of_<char style="nd">god</char>, the holiness of_you_all, to_be_keeping_away you_all from sexual_immorality, <verse eid="1TH 4:3" /><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1TH 4:4" />to_have_known each of_you_all the of_himself vessel, to_be_acquiring in holiness and honour, <verse eid="1TH 4:4" /><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1TH 4:5" />not in <char style="add">+the</char>_passion of_lust, just_as also the pagans not having_known <char style="nd">god</char>, <verse eid="1TH 4:5" /><verse number="6" style="v" sid="1TH 4:6" />not to_be_going_beyond and to_be_exploiting in the matter the brother of_him, because avenging <char style="add">=is</char> <char style="add">+the</char>_<char style="nd">master</char> concerning all these <char style="add">&gt;things</char>, as also we_previously_said to_you_all and we_testified. <verse eid="1TH 4:6" /><verse number="7" style="v" sid="1TH 4:7" />For not called us <char style="nd">god</char> to impurity, but in holiness. <verse eid="1TH 4:7" /><verse number="8" style="v" sid="1TH 4:8" />So_then the <char style="add">&gt;one</char> rejecting <char style="add">this</char>, not <char style="add">+a</char>_human is_rejecting, but <char style="nd">god</char>, the <char style="add">&gt;one</char> giving the <char style="nd">spirit</char> of_him holy to you_all. <verse eid="1TH 4:8" /><verse number="9" style="v" sid="1TH 4:9" />And concerning brotherly_love, no need you_all_are_having <char style="add">for_me</char> to_be_writing to_you_all, for yourselves you_all god-taught are, in_order that to_be_loving one_another. <verse eid="1TH 4:9" /><verse number="10" style="v" sid="1TH 4:10" />For also you_all_are_doing it toward all the brothers, who <char style="add">=are</char> in all Makedonia. But we_are_exhorting you_all, brothers, to_be_abounding more, <verse eid="1TH 4:10" /><verse number="11" style="v" sid="1TH 4:11" />and to_be_being_ambitious to_be_living_quietly and to_be_doing your own <char style="add">&gt;things</char>, and to_be_working with_your own hands of_you_all, as to_you_all we_commanded, <verse eid="1TH 4:11" /><verse number="12" style="v" sid="1TH 4:12" />in_order_that you_all_may_be_walking properly toward the <char style="add">&gt;ones</char> outside, and of_nothing need you_all_may_be_having. <verse eid="1TH 4:12" /><verse number="13" style="v" sid="1TH 4:13" />Not but we_are_wanting you_all to_be_not_knowing, brothers, concerning the <char style="add">&gt;ones</char> being_fallen_asleep, in_order_that not you_all _may_be_being_sorrowed, as also the rest, the <char style="add">&gt;ones</char> not having hope. <verse eid="1TH 4:13" /><verse number="14" style="v" sid="1TH 4:14" />For if we_are_believing that <char style="nd">Yaʸsous/(Yəhōshūˊa)</char> died_off and rose_up, thus also <char style="nd">god</char> the <char style="add">&gt;ones</char> having_been_fallen_asleep through <char style="nd">Yaʸsous</char> will_be_bringing with him. <verse eid="1TH 4:14" /><verse number="15" style="v" sid="1TH 4:15" />For this to_you_all we_are_saying in <char style="add">+the</char>_message of_<char style="add">+the</char>_<char style="nd">master</char>, that we the <char style="add">&gt;ones</char> living, being_remaining to the coming of_the <char style="nd">master</char>, by_no_means not may_precede the <char style="add">&gt;ones</char> having_been_fallen_asleep. <verse eid="1TH 4:15" /><verse number="16" style="v" sid="1TH 4:16" />Because himself the <char style="nd">master</char> with <char style="add">+a</char>_loud_command, with <char style="add">+the</char>_voice of_<char style="add">+an</char>_archangel, and with <char style="add">+the</char>_trumpet of_<char style="nd">god</char>, will_be_coming_downhill from heaven, and the dead in <char style="nd">chosen_one/messiah</char> will_be_rising_up first, <verse eid="1TH 4:16" /><verse number="17" style="v" sid="1TH 4:17" />then we the <char style="add">&gt;ones</char> living, being_remaining together with them, will_be_being_snatched in <char style="add">+the</char>_clouds for <char style="add">+the</char>_meeting of_the <char style="nd">master</char> in <char style="add">+the</char>_air, and thus always with <char style="add">+the</char>_<char style="nd">master</char> we_will_be. <verse eid="1TH 4:17" /><verse number="18" style="v" sid="1TH 4:18" />So_then be_comforting one_another with messages these.<chapter eid="1TH 4" /><chapter number="5" style="c" sid="1TH 5" /><verse eid="1TH 4:18" /><verse number="1" style="v" sid="1TH 5:1" />And concerning the times and the seasons, brothers, no need you_all_are_having to_you_all to_be_being_written. <verse eid="1TH 5:1" /><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1TH 5:2" />For yourselves exactly you_all_have_known that <char style="add">+the</char>_day of_<char style="add">+the</char>_<char style="nd">master</char>, as <char style="add">+a</char>_thief by night thus is_coming. <verse eid="1TH 5:2" /><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1TH 5:3" />Whenever they_may_be_saying: Peace and security, then sudden is_recognizing to_them destruction, as the birth_pains to_the <char style="add">woman</char> in pregnant having <char style="add">a_child</char>, and by_no_means not they_may_escape. <verse eid="1TH 5:3" /><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1TH 5:4" />But you_all, brothers, not are in darkness, in_order_that the day you_all like thieves may_grasp. <verse eid="1TH 5:4" /><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1TH 5:5" />For all you_all sons of_light are, and sons of_day. Neither we_are of_night nor of_darkness. <verse eid="1TH 5:5" /><verse number="6" style="v" sid="1TH 5:6" />Therefore consequently not we_may_be_sleeping as the rest, but we_may_be_watching and we_may_be_being_sober. <verse eid="1TH 5:6" /><verse number="7" style="v" sid="1TH 5:7" />For the <char style="add">&gt;ones</char> sleeping, by_night are_sleeping, and the <char style="add">&gt;ones</char> being_drunk, by_night are_being_drunk. <verse eid="1TH 5:7" /><verse number="8" style="v" sid="1TH 5:8" />But we of_<char style="add">+the</char>_day being, may_be_being_sober, having_dressed_in <char style="add">+the</char>_breastplate of_faith and love, and <char style="add">+the</char>_helmet, <char style="add">+the</char>_hope of_salvation. <verse eid="1TH 5:8" /><verse number="9" style="v" sid="1TH 5:9" />Because not appointed <char style="nd">god</char> us for severe_anger, but for procuring of_salvation through the <char style="nd">master</char> of_us, <char style="nd">Yaʸsous</char> <verse eid="1TH 5:9" /><verse number="10" style="v" sid="1TH 5:10" />the <char style="add">&gt;one</char> having_died_off for us, in_order_that whether we_may_be_watching or we_may_be_sleeping, together with him we_may_live. <verse eid="1TH 5:10" /><verse number="11" style="v" sid="1TH 5:11" />Therefore be_comforting one_another, and be_building one one, as also you_all_are_doing. <verse eid="1TH 5:11" /><verse number="12" style="v" sid="1TH 5:12" />But we_are_asking you_all, brothers, to_have_known the <char style="add">&gt;ones</char> laboring among you_all, and leading of_you_all in <char style="add">+the</char>_<char style="nd">master</char>, and admonishing you_all, <verse eid="1TH 5:12" /><verse number="13" style="v" sid="1TH 5:13" />and to_be_considering them beyond_exceedingly in love, because_of the work of_them. Be_being_at_peace among yourselves. <verse eid="1TH 5:13" /><verse number="14" style="v" sid="1TH 5:14" />And we_are_exhorting you_all, brothers, be_admonishing the lazy, be_consoling the fainthearted, be_upholding of_the weak, be_being_patient toward all. <verse eid="1TH 5:14" /><verse number="15" style="v" sid="1TH 5:15" />Be_seeing not someone evil for evil to_anyone may_give_back, but always the good be_pursuing, and toward one_another and toward all. <verse eid="1TH 5:15" /><verse number="16" style="v" sid="1TH 5:16" />Always be_rejoicing. <verse eid="1TH 5:16" /><verse number="17" style="v" sid="1TH 5:17" />Unceasingly be_praying. <verse eid="1TH 5:17" /><verse number="18" style="v" sid="1TH 5:18" />In everything be_giving_thanks, for this <char style="add">=is</char> <char style="add">+the</char>_will of_<char style="nd">god</char> in <char style="nd">chosen_one/messiah</char> <char style="nd">Yaʸsous/(Yəhōshūˊa)</char> toward you_all. <verse eid="1TH 5:18" /><verse number="19" style="v" sid="1TH 5:19" />The <char style="nd">spirit</char> not be_extinguishing. <verse eid="1TH 5:19" /><verse number="20" style="v" sid="1TH 5:20" />Prophesies not be_scorning. <verse eid="1TH 5:20" /><verse number="21" style="v" sid="1TH 5:21" />All <char style="add">&gt;things</char> be_approving, the good be_keeping. <verse eid="1TH 5:21" /><verse number="22" style="v" sid="1TH 5:22" />From every appearance of_evil be_keeping_away. <verse eid="1TH 5:22" /><verse number="23" style="v" sid="1TH 5:23" />And himself <char style="nd">god</char> of_peace might_sanctify you_all complete, and complete of_you_all the spirit, and soul, and body, blamelessly at the coming of_the <char style="nd">master</char> of_us, <char style="nd">Yaʸsous</char> <char style="nd">chosen_one</char>, might_have_kept. <verse eid="1TH 5:23" /><verse number="24" style="v" sid="1TH 5:24" />Faithful <char style="add">=is</char> the <char style="add">&gt;one</char> calling you_all, who also will_be_performing <char style="add">it</char>. <verse eid="1TH 5:24" /><verse number="25" style="v" sid="1TH 5:25" />Brothers, be_praying also for us. <verse eid="1TH 5:25" /><verse number="26" style="v" sid="1TH 5:26" />Greet the brothers all with <char style="add">+a</char>_kiss holy. <verse eid="1TH 5:26" /><verse number="27" style="v" sid="1TH 5:27" />I_am_adjuring you_all by_the <char style="nd">master</char>, to_be_read my letter to_all the brothers. <verse eid="1TH 5:27" /><verse number="28" style="v" sid="1TH 5:28" />The grace of_the <char style="nd">master</char> of_us, <char style="nd">Yaʸsous</char> <char style="nd">chosen_one</char>, with you_all <char style="add">be</char>. Truly.<chapter eid="1TH 5" /></usx>